(=H1 Login H1=)
(=P
To login to LiveJournal, enter your username and password below.  <B>New Users:</B> Go <a href="/create.bml">create an account</a>: it's free, simple, causes less cavities than leading brands, and guaranteed to make you more attractive to the opposite sex. P=)
(=P You may also specify when your login expires.  By default your login will expire when you close your browser, which is best on public computers.  However, if you're the only user of your computer and nobody else has access to it, you may choose to remain logged in forever.
P=)

<FORM ACTION="login_do.bml" METHOD="POST">

