(=H1 Why login? H1=)
(=P
There are some of the main benefits of logging in:
<UL>
<LI>You won't have to enter your username/password anywhere on the site anymore.
<LI>You'll be able to view "protected" journal entries from your friends that give you access to read them.
<LI>A lot of features are only visible or accessible when you're logged in.
</UL>
P=)

